text: Ambroise Sarr was a wrestler from Senegal. Sarr competed at the 1976, 1980, 1984 and the 1988 Summer Olympics. He was born on 14 December 1950.Ambroise Sarr == References == Category:1950 births Category:2024 deaths Category:Senegalese wrestlers Category:Olympians for Senegal
